				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p>Yay 100% completed. If your VPS does not build completely you are either missing some libraries needed to build or there is another issue going on. Please reach out on one of our social platforms to get some additional help. Once the binaries have been successfully built, we need to move to the folder and copy the binaries to an easier location to access:</p>					</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-f3ef0a9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-code-highlight" data-id="f3ef0a9" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="code-highlight.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<div class="prismjs-tomorrow copy-to-clipboard ">
