				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-07a9995 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="07a9995" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p>Now that we are at the main folder location we can create a new folder on the desktop for ease of access to our Arqma binaries:</p>					</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a8b3346 elementor-widget elementor-widget-code-highlight" data-id="a8b3346" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="code-highlight.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
