			<pre data-line="" class="highlight-height language-markup ">
				<code readonly="true" class="language-markup">
					<xmp>mkdir runme
## you can name this whatever you want like 'mkdir catsRcute' or something you like</xmp>
				</code>
			</pre>
		</div>
				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-19331c2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="19331c2" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p>Now let’s copy the built binaries to the new folder we created:</p>					</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-192b879 elementor-widget elementor-widget-code-highlight" data-id="192b879" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="code-highlight.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<div class="prismjs-tomorrow copy-to-clipboard ">
			<pre data-line="" class="highlight-height language-markup ">
				<code readonly="true" class="language-markup">
					<xmp>cp ~/arqma/build/release/bin/* ~/runme</xmp>
				</code>
			</pre>
		</div>
				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d6c8627 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="d6c8627" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
